                <p>
                    tiruvāy-k kēḻvi muṉṉ-āka tiripuvaṉa-c-cakkaravattikaḷ <unclear>ma</unclear>turaiyum pāṇṭiyaṉ muṭi-t-talaiyuṅ ko<unclear>ṇṭ-aruḷiya</unclear>
                    <lb n="2"/><hi rend="grantha"><unclear>śrī</unclear></hi>-kulōttuṅka-<unclear>cōḻa</unclear>-<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>vaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="20">2 <g type="numeral">10</g></num> vatu <gap reason="illegible" quantity="20" unit="character" precision="low"/> peṟṟa <gap reason="illegible" quantity="5" unit="character" precision="low"/> ṭa
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/>cōḻa-maṇṭalattu kāliyūṟ-k-kōṭṭattu viṟppēṭṭu nāṭṭu karitaṭuttūr-āṉa <hi rend="grantha">hasti</hi>-nivāraṇa<!--EF: nivirāṇa?-->-c-catu<hi rend="grantha"><unclear>rvvedi</unclear></hi>-maṅka<unclear>la</unclear>ttu <gap reason="illegible" quantity="10" unit="character" precision="low"/> <unclear>tiru</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" quantity="5" unit="character" precision="low"/> <supplied reason="lost"> catu</supplied><hi rend="grantha">rvve</hi>
                    <lb n="4"/><hi rend="grantha">di</hi>-maṅkalattu                    
                    
                    k<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>ī</reg></choice>ḻ-pāṟk’ ellai vaṭak<seg rend="check">kilē toṇ</seg> <gap reason="illegible" quantity="30" unit="character" precision="low"/> kā<supplied reason="lost">lu</supplied>kku teṟkum <gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="5" break="no"/>ḷāḷap peruñ ceṟu muḷ maṭai<seg rend="check">kku</seg> teṟkku ṉōkkiṉa kaṇāṟṟu <gap reason="illegible" quantity="30" unit="character" precision="low"/> Ik-kaṇṇā
                    <lb n="6" break="no"/>ṟṟu-c cevvai teṟkkil varampu<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied><unclear>ku</unclear> mēṟkkum y-i-varampu mēṟkku ṉōkki teṉ maṭal vaḷaivāḷ taricuṟṟu vaḷaiyaḷ Ēri mēlkaṭai <gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="character"/> mēṟkkum <gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="7" break="no"/>ṇṭāra kuḷamum k<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>ī</reg></choice>ḻmēl ka<seg rend="check">vu</seg>tēva Ōṭai karaikkum mēlai-k karaikkuḻikku vaṭakkum cetarāy-p puttēri Ēta vāyivā mēlai Accaṅ kuḻikku kiḻakkum vaṭa
                    
                    <!--Resume check from here-->
                    <lb n="8" break="no"/>kīḻaip puṟṟu naṭu vērikkuḷā pāccalāṉa cētarāyaṉ kālukku-k kiḻakkum Ik-kāl-c cevvai vaṭakkalēriyil-p pāṭṭa<unclear>ṉ</unclear> maṇ puṟṟu vaṭakki
                    <lb n="9" break="no"/>l iraṇṭu Uṟa-k kiḻakkum
                    
                    vaṭa-pāṟk’ellai <unclear>Āṟu</unclear> naṭu Uṟavum vaṭa kiḻakku muṟuṭṭu-p paṭṭikku mēṟkkum teṉ maṭalānā <hi rend="bold">bhentra</hi>n kaṇṇāṟu parappāṉa
                    <lb n="10"/>paṭṭa teṟkkil kulai-k-karai mēṟkkum Ik-kiḻakku ṉōkkiṉa kulai-k-karai kavaṟ-k-kāluṟku teṟkkum
                    
                    I-nāṟkk’ ellaikku Uḷppaṭa n<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>ī</reg></choice>r nilamum ko
                    <lb n="11" break="no"/>llai nilamum kāṭ’ eḻu karampum cētarāyap puttēri<unclear>yam</unclear> vaṭakkil ēyil teṟkkiṟ tūmpum Ivv-akarattukku <hi rend="grantha">so</hi>mākavum <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kku-p paḷḷa
                    <lb n="12" break="no"/>t tūmpum matakum Āṟṟu-k kāl Iraṇṭu maccakkālum Ivattāl nālattoru nīr <hi rend="grantha">prāpti</hi>kaḷum maṟṟum Ivaṟṟil viḷai <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kaḷum Uḷppaṭa
                    <lb n="13"/>Ivv-akarattu <hi rend="grantha">brāhma</hi>ṇar nālppattu Iruvaṟkum y-iraṇṭu pērkaḷ Akaram-āka y-iṭṭu cilālēkai paṇṇi-k kuṭuttōm Aṉṟātu kā<unclear>cu</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ce <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/>
                </p>
